    "body": "What about we remove the `urlSync` option right away (we are in beta, that's the right time)? In the react-world there is a high probability people will want to use a custom routing solution rather than ours.\n\nThe example you created provides a nicer interface and allow more customization easily (like doing `/search/some+products?filters=..` or renaming any parameter).\n",
